      "name": "FEA compression-bending prediction claim for non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw",
      "description": "The FEA model ensemble accurately predicts ASTM F1717 static compression-bending behavior (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement) of the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct within pre-established acceptance bounds.",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/vr-cb-stiffness-yield",
