      "description": "Raw load-displacement data from N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested under ASTM F1717 static compression-bending protocol at two independent laboratories. Includes stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement for each specimen.",
